{"tid":602830,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【割地兩檢】主要工程竣工 高鐵列車命名「動感號」","createTime":"2018-03-23T08:44:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-23T09:03:36.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3d93291e33311531798bb0a26aa37817dd53c533","tid":602830,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T08:44:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180323/large/1521794417_72d0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180323%2Flarge%2F1521794417_72d0.png&h=a82b52dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港鐵舉行高鐵香港段項目主要工程竣工典禮，特首林鄭月娥由石崗乘搭高鐵到西九站出席典禮。她致詞時形容8分鐘車程中，行車穩定，車廂寧靜、寛敞，重申指高鐵香港段距通車僅一步之遙，只差「一地兩檢」三步走的最後一步立法工作，再次呼籲立法會以務實態度審議一地兩檢條例草案，令高鐵盡快通車。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵主席馬時亨則指，主體工程進度為99%，下月開始會與各部門開始測試，包括試營運，望立法會通過一地兩檢，於今年9月通車。西九車站中庭售票處至少26個櫃位大致完成，每個櫃位均設電腦，而售票處4個LED大型屏幕，其中2個已安裝。<br />\n<br />\n至於港鐵早前舉辦的高鐵列車命名比賽揭曉，將命名為「動感號」，英文為「Vibrant Express」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180323/57985720\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180323%2F57985720&d=hNXgKv16K%2FAoYbsNLvoNVdU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=2f72d6be\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180323%2F57985720&h=254f727d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180323/57985720</a>"},{"pid":"c10c3e0ef6b736e78d96974d33a73e018412ee20","tid":602830,"uid":4826,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T08:45:44.000Z","msg":"吉祥物<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/23/164542_fe3160567d3870ed866e91befc46c668.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F23%2F164542_fe3160567d3870ed866e91befc46c668.png&h=654a22eb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fb68854194db1c734f607580a0a617e0ad3c6583","tid":602830,"uid":33456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T08:46:19.000Z","msg":"動感號<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"034932d2718f7834e2a47addaf8c7bf4b1acc391","tid":602830,"uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T08:51:53.000Z","msg":"動撚號"},{"pid":"7ca98477953c1a26ff4e989fa5e2bf740a06ba54","tid":602830,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T08:53:11.000Z","msg":"賭撚號"},{"pid":"1fe9c15c2b5273c0d40632c00c59068b7dab66d4","tid":602830,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T08:56:32.000Z","msg":"留名睇 Vibrant 變 Vibrate 直至解體 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"510d278610f714b1910a412bab1528908f3afd8d","tid":602830,"uid":82657,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T09:02:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/23/170226_b188c473dd68dc6753c7021c8dcb4ea1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F23%2F170226_b188c473dd68dc6753c7021c8dcb4ea1.png&h=44d3f349&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屌你d 優異獎好撚垃圾"},{"pid":"96526fb0b8cc786fbb2b24c285d702894f60b36e","tid":602830,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T09:03:36.000Z","msg":"炒車嗰陣就唔慌唔動感"}]}